Do not rent here. It will stress you out more than you know. Horrible units, horrible maintenance and horrible agents that are not willing to help. They can't get a complaint whatsoever because they think you're yelling at them and "refuse" to be talked to in that way. When all you are trying to do is file a work order, and you are trying to ask why nothing had been done....

For tenants who lives here, and is having trouble with your unit and have made attempts to the office for issues like leaks, mold or electrical, Pls call the city for building inspectors to come and take a look. Or call and ask for the tenants rights number to make a complaint.
